INSTALL:
	Two external libraries will need to be installed:
	* python-bson library (for sending bson objects through the sockets)
	  install by typing:
		$ sudo apt-get install python-bson
	* bitarray 0.8.1 library (for easier bit manipulation)
	  install by typing:
		$ wget https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/b/bitarray/bitarray-0.8.1.tar.gz
		$ tar xvf bitarray-0.8.1.tar.gz
		$ cd bitarray-0.8.1/
		$ python setup.py
